text: Good for quick south Indian (veg) breakfast options. Breakfast usually gets over by 9:30 - 10:00 AM. Best to have before then

The briyani is very nice but sadly it’s close already.
Any one know where’s its relocated?

Surprised with quality and the taste.
I tried the briyani with prawns and another day with the fish.

Both were good. The briyani was flavourful!
Food options are good, especially Indian vegetarian. The preparation & taste is excellent. Nice ambience except that the food court is non-aircon.
They serve not fresh oily papadum. Briyani Mutton full of bones and fats
